OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry night
OL,6,Fin the west with long clear spells. In
OL,7,Fthe east it will be cloudy with a few
OL,8,Fshowers possible over Lothian and
OL,9,FBorders. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FSunny spells in the west
OL,12,Fduring the morning, cloudier with a
OL,13,Ffew showers in the east. Cloud
OL,14,Fspreading west in the afternoon, with
OL,15,Fthe chance of a few light showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
